OL,5, The former Post Office chairman has    
OL,6, shocked MPs by claiming that the       
OL,7, company's current chief executive Nick 
OL,8, Read is under investigation.           
OL,10,FHenry Staunton made the allegation at a
OL,11,Fhearing to discuss compensation        
OL,12,Fpayments to sub-postmasters at the     
OL,13,Fcentre of the Horizon scandal.         
OL,15,FAlan Bates, the inspiration behind the 
OL,16,FITV drama, told MPs the government     
OL,17,Fneeded to "get on and pay people".     
OL,19,FThe Post Office has been contacted for 
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
